      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 13 article about impending sale of Connecticut Post</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Thursday about the impending sale of The Connecticut Post, the daily newspaper in Bridgeport, misstated its circulation ranking in the state. The Post is No. 3 -- behind The Hartford Courant as well as The New Haven Register -- not No. 2.</p>
      </block>
